So there exists [a bug in Vert.x][1] that causes issues with `CompositeFuture.all(listoffutures)`, etc., at least in JDK 17, if `listoffutures` is of type `List&lt;Future&lt;SomeType&gt;&gt;` (or `List&lt;Future&lt;?&gt;&gt;`).

This bug might get fixed in Vert.x 5.

