I&#39;m running into a similar issue, as far as I can tell you have to deal with the error handling yourself. My solution is to update the UI via a method call:

Something like:

      try
      {
        //blah...
      }
      catch (Exception e)
      {
        reportAndLogException(e);
      }
      ...
      public void reportAndLogException(final Throwable t)
      {
        Platform.runLater(new Runnable() {
